Big Brother Naija, BBNaija, housemate Mike, has emerged winner of the Arena Games. Ebuka Obi-Uchendu announced this on Sunday during BBNaija final eviction show. Mike as the winner of Arena Friday games won N2m naira. One of housemates among Mike, Mercy, and Frodd will emerge winner of N60m grand prize The 2019 edition, tagged ‘Pepper Dem’, commenced June 30, 2019 with 26 housemates and was aired for 99 days. Big Brother Naija is the fourth season of Nigerian version of the reality show. BB Naija witnessed drama, emotion, betrayal and intrigues while the show lasted. Nigerian music stars including Tiwa Savage, MI Abaga and Patoranking performed at the live show. Download Daily Post App.    Subscribe to Daily Post Newsletter.    Advertise with us.   Send us enquiries, press releases.